Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.93,0:00:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（老公不知道的淫乱的爱妻）\N（把网球部的教练带回家）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.66,0:00:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（做爱 森泽佳奈）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.68,0:00:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老公一直加班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.88,0:00:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不关心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.15,0:00:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都是那么无聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.02,0:00:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就加入了网球部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.96,0:00:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次感觉心情好了点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.64,0:00:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这里的教练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.04,0:00:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.51,0:00:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们保持着不正当的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.88,0:02:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.28,0:02:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.02,0:02:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打网球吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.02,0:02:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.95,0:02:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点运动不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.42,0:02:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我打不好给大家添麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.50,0:02:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.63,0:02:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅长运动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.04,0:02:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 教练很温柔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.11,0:03:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话一起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.58,0:03:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说的话\N我就加入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.38,0:03:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定\N一起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.72,0:03:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅长运动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.85,0:03:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变主意了就联系我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.93,0:03:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.20,0:03:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.26,0:03:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.50,0:05:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天只有这个了
